commit.message:
m68k.c (init_FPA_table): Provide static prototype.

	* m68k.c (init_FPA_table): Provide static prototype.
	* mips/abi64.h (mips_function_value): Move prototype to ...
	* mips-protos.h (mips_function_value): ... here.
	* mips.c: Include halfpic.h.
	* output.h (rdata_section): Prototype.

From-SVN: r47516
